name: WEEBS
description: Weebs App is the Web3 Marketplace for Anime-Comic-Gaming industry. Weebs token is aimed to enable cross-border transaction through defi and increase monetization channels of creators through its Cosplay-To-Earn model. Weebs also enables exclusive merchandise creation via voting and staking. Its WeebsVerse powers up Creators and fans engagements through virtual meet & greet. Weebs is aimed to be the largest ACG marketplace in the world.
